data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Welcome to your idyllic haven in the heart of natural beauty, nestled in the sought-after region between Gainesville and Ocala, Florida. This enchanting 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home exudes a sense of warmth, character, and endless possibilities.    As you approach along the oak-lined driveway, a sense of tranquility envelops you. The timeless charm of this home is enhanced by a cleverly converted garage, now a versatile den/extra bedroom, offering flexibility for your unique lifestyle needs.    The exterior of the home is framed by majestic oak trees that cast dappled sunlight, creating a serene backdrop for outdoor activities. The fenced backyard is a haven for your furry friends and feathered companions, a safe space for pets and even a playful flock of chickens, embodying the spirit of rural living.    Zoned A1, this property offers you the freedom to cultivate your vision of an agrarian lifestyle. Whether you dream of a bountiful garden, a small orchard, or a homestead with a few animals, the possibilities are boundless.    Nature lovers will rejoice at the proximity to nearby springs and the expansive Three State Forest, providing endless opportunities for exploration, hiking, and communing with the great outdoors. And for those yearning for a coastal escape, the allure of the beach is just a short drive away – less than two hours to either the Atlantic or Gulf Coast.    Step outside, where the canvas of your dreams awaits. An RV barn stands ready to shelter your mobile adventures, while an additional shed offers the perfect space to stow your lawn equipment, ensuring your property remains pristine and organized.    Inside, the heart of the home is a gally kitchen complete with a charming nook – a welcoming space for culinary creations and heartwarming conversations. The split floor plan ensures privacy, with the master suite boasting a walk-in shower for a touch of luxury.    This residence is more than just a home; it's an embodiment of the Florida lifestyle you've always imagined. A harmonious blend of comfort and opportunity, convenience and nature, space and intimacy. Embrace the freedom of country living, while still being just a stone's throw from the cultural and urban amenities of nearby cities.    Discover the joy of waking up to the rustling leaves, exploring nearby springs, and relaxing under the shade of your very own oak trees. This property is not just a house; it's an invitation to live your dreams. Come, seize the moment, and make this haven your own.
